{
  "texts": [
    "An artificially intelligent poll is driven by machine learning and powered by Big Data.",
    "This paper focuses specifically on pre-election opinion-polling.",
    "Early adoption of this new technology has already had a noticeable societal impact.",
    "In the 2017 UK General Election, YouGov's AI-polls were the most accurate, and their publication affected currency markets, with the £ losing 0.5% of its value as a result of shifts in expectations (Lauderdale et al. 2020).",
    "And yet this technology in its existing form is still in its early stage."
  ]
}